{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %} About us {% endblock %}
{% block body %}
<h2>About Us</h2>
    <div class="content">
        <article>

            <p>This little corner of the internet started with a simple thought: wishes are better when they're shared.</p>

            <p>We all have that list—the bungee jump, the northern lights, the perfect baklava, the concert tickets we've been eyeing for months. Some wishes feel a bit scary to do alone. Others just seem more fun with company. </p>

            <p>So we built a cozy little space where you can share your wishes, see who else dreams of the same things, and maybe—just maybe—find a few kindred spirits to join you.</p>

            <p>That's it, really. No algorithms trying to sell you things. No pressure to be social. Just real people, real wishes, and the gentle nudge to say: "Hey, I want to do that too. Want to go together?"</p>

            <p>This is a side project I'm building bit by bit, and honestly? I'm having a lot of fun with it. It's not trying to be a big deal—just a small, honest place to connect over the things that make life feel full.</p>

            <p>If you're here, I hope you find exactly what you're looking for. A wish granted. A new friend. Or just the simple joy of knowing you're not the only one who wants to sandboard down a dune.</p>

            <p>Let's share some wishes.✨

        </article>
    </div>

{% endblock %}
{% block extrastyle %}
    <style>
        body{

            background-image: url('{{ asset('images/7023263.jpg') }}'), linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)) ;
        }
        footer{
            margin-top: 10vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6));
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding:4px;
        }
    </style>
{% endblock %}

